msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.4.22"
msgid "“anārambho hotū”ti."
msgstr "where no harm will be done. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.4.23"
msgid "“Saparikkamano hotū”ti,"
msgstr "which has a space on all sides. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.4.24"
msgid "anāpatti."
msgstr "There is no offense."

#. HTML: </p><h5>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.5.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Offenses for appointed builders"

#. HTML: </h5><p>
#. REF: sc35, pts-cs-bu-ss7.3.5, ms1V_1546 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.5.1"
msgid "Bhikkhu samādisitvā pakkamati—"
msgstr "A monk appoints someone"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.5.2"
msgid "“vihāraṃ me karothā”ti."
msgstr "to build him a dwelling and then departs."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.5.3"
msgid "Samādisati ca—"
msgstr "He tells them"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.5.4"
msgid "“desitavatthuko ca hotu anārambho ca saparikkamano cā”ti."
msgstr "to build one whose site has been approved, where no harm will be done, and which has a space on all sides."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.5.5"
msgid "Tassa vihāraṃ karonti adesi­ta­vatthu­kaṃ sārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ, āpatti kārukānaṃ tiṇṇaṃ dukkaṭānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "If they build one whose site has not been approved, where harm will be done, and which lacks a space on all sides, the builders commit three offenses of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.5.6"
msgid "sārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti kārukānaṃ dvinnaṃ dukkaṭānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "where harm will be done, but which has a space on all sides, the builders commit two offenses of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.5.7"
msgid "anārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ, āpatti kārukānaṃ dvinnaṃ dukkaṭānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "where no harm will be done, but which lacks a space on all sides, the builders commit two offenses of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.5.8"
msgid "anārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti kārukānaṃ dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "where no harm will be done, and which has a space on all sides, the builders commit one offense of wrong conduct."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc36, ms1V_1547 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.5.9"
msgid "Bhikkhu samādisitvā pakkamati—"
msgstr "A monk appoints someone"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.5.10"
msgid "“vihāraṃ me karothā”ti."
msgstr "to build him a dwelling and then departs."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.5.11"
msgid "Samādisati ca—"
msgstr "He tells them"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.5.12"
msgid "“desitavatthuko ca hotu anārambho ca saparikkamano cā”ti."
msgstr "to build one whose site has been approved, where no harm will be done, and which has a space on all sides."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.5.13"
msgid "Tassa vihāraṃ karonti desita­vatthu­kaṃ sārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ, āpatti kārukānaṃ dvinnaṃ dukkaṭānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "If they build one whose site has been approved, where harm will be done, and which lacks a space on all sides, the builders commit two offenses of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.5.14"
msgid "sārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti kārukānaṃ dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr "where harm will be done, but which has a space on all sides, the builders commit one offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.5.15"
msgid "anārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ, āpatti kārukānaṃ dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr "where no harm will be done, but which lacks a space on all sides, the builders commit one offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.5.16"
msgid "anārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, anāpatti."
msgstr "where no harm will be done, and which has a space on all sides, there is no offense."

#. HTML: </p><h5>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.6.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Unfinished when he returns"

#. HTML: </h5><p>
#. REF: sc37, pts-cs-bu-ss7.3.6, ms1V_1548 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.6.1"
msgid "Bhikkhu samādisitvā pakkamati—"
msgstr "A monk appoints someone"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.6.2"
msgid "“vihāraṃ me karothā”ti."
msgstr "to build him a dwelling and then departs."

#. REF: pts-vp-en1.270
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.6.3"
msgid "Tassa vihāraṃ karonti adesi­ta­vatthu­kaṃ sārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ."
msgstr "They build one whose site has not been approved, where harm will be done, and which lacks a space on all sides."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.6.4"
msgid "So ce vippakate āgacchati, tena bhikkhunā so vihāro aññassa vā dātabbo bhinditvā vā puna kātabbo."
msgstr "If it is unfinished when he returns, that dwelling is to be given to someone else, or it is to be demolished and rebuilt."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.6.5"
msgid "No ce aññassa vā dadeyya bhinditvā vā puna kāreyya, āpatti saṃghādisesena dvinnaṃ dukkaṭānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "If he does not give it to someone else, or does not demolish and rebuild it, he commits one offense entailing suspension and two offenses of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.6.6"
msgid "sārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti saṃghādisesena dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr "where harm will be done, but which has a space on all sides, he commits one offense entailing suspension and one offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.6.7"
msgid "anārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ, āpatti saṃghādisesena dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr "where no harm will be done, but which lacks a space on all sides, he commits one offense entailing suspension and one offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.6.8"
msgid "anārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr "where no harm will be done, and which has a space on all sides, he commits one offense entailing suspension."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc38, ms1V_1549 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.6.9"
msgid "Bhikkhu samādisitvā pakkamati—"
msgstr "A monk appoints someone"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.6.10"
msgid "“vihāraṃ me karothā”ti."
msgstr "to build him a dwelling and then departs."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.6.11"
msgid "Tassa vihāraṃ karonti desita­vatthu­kaṃ sārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ."
msgstr "They build one whose site has been approved, where harm will be done, and which lacks a space on all sides."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.6.12"
msgid "So ce vippakate āgacchati, tena bhikkhunā so vihāro aññassa vā dātabbo bhinditvā vā puna kātabbo."
msgstr "If it is unfinished when he returns, that dwelling is to be given to someone else, or it is to be demolished and rebuilt."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.6.13"
msgid "No ce aññassa vā dadeyya bhinditvā vā puna kāreyya, āpatti dvinnaṃ dukkaṭānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "If he does not give it to someone else, or does not demolish and rebuild it, he commits two offenses of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.6.14"
msgid "sārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr "where harm will be done, but which has a space on all sides, he commits one offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.6.15"
msgid "anārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ, āpatti dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr "where no harm will be done, but which lacks a space on all sides, he commits one offense of wrong conduct. …"

