msgstr "where no harm will be done, and which has a space on all sides, there is no offense."

#. HTML: </p><h3>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.7.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Permutations part 2"

#. HTML: </h3><p>
#. REF: sc39, pts-cs-bu-ss7.3.7, ms1V_1550 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.7.1"
msgid "Attanā vippakataṃ attanā pariyosāpeti, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr "If he finishes what he began himself, he commits an offense entailing suspension."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc40, ms1V_1551 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.7.2"
msgid "Attanā vippakataṃ parehi pariyosāpeti, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr "If he gets others to finish what he began himself, he commits an offense entailing suspension."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc41, ms1V_1552 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.7.3"
msgid "Parehi vippakataṃ attanā pariyosāpeti, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr "If he finishes himself what was begun by others, he commits an offense entailing suspension."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc42, ms1V_1553 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.7.4"
msgid "Parehi vippakataṃ parehi pariyosāpeti, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr "If he gets others to finish what was begun by others, he commits an offense entailing suspension."

#. HTML: </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.7.4a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Non-offenses"

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: sc43, ms1V_1554 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.7.5"
msgid "Anāpatti—"
msgstr "There is no offense:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.7.6"
msgid "leṇe guhāya tiṇakuṭikāya"
msgstr "if it is a shelter, if it is a cave, if it is a grass hut;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.7.7"
msgid "aññassatthāya vāsāgāraṃ ṭhapetvā"
msgstr "if it is built for someone else;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.7.8"
msgid "sabbattha."
msgstr "if it is anything apart from a dwelling;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.7.9"
msgid "Anāpatti ummattakassa,"
msgstr "if he is insane;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.7.10"
msgid "ādi­kammi­kas­sāti."
msgstr "if he is the first offender."

#. HTML: </p><hr><p class="endsutta">
#. REF: sc44, ms1V_1555 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:3.7.11"
msgid "Vihāra­kāra­sikkhā­padaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ sattamaṃ."
msgstr "The seventh rule, the training rule on building dwellings, is finished."
